<xhtml:div xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
           class="xforms-error-panel xforms-initially-hidden">
    <xhtml:div class="hd">An error has occurred</xhtml:div>
    <xhtml:div class="bd">
        <xhtml:p>
            An error has occurred in Orbeon Forms. You may want to try the following:
        </xhtml:p>
        <xhtml:ul>
            <xhtml:li>Close this dialog and continue to use this page.</xhtml:li>
            <xhtml:li>If this does not work, press the <code>ctrl</code> key (or <code>command</code> key on a Mac) and click on the Reload button in the toolbar.</xhtml:li>
            <xhtml:li>Return <xhtml:a href="/">home</xhtml:a>.</xhtml:li>
        </xhtml:ul>
        <xhtml:div class="xforms-error-panel-details-hidden">
            <xhtml:p>
                <xhtml:a class="xforms-error-panel-show-details">
                    <xhtml:img src="/ops/images/xforms/section-closed.png"/>
                    <xhtml:span>Show details</xhtml:span>
                </xhtml:a>
            </xhtml:p>
        </xhtml:div>
        <xhtml:div class="xforms-error-panel-details-shown xforms-disabled">
            <xhtml:p>
                <xhtml:a class="xforms-error-panel-hide-details">
                    <xhtml:img src="/ops/images/xforms/section-opened.png"/>
                    <xhtml:span>Hide details</xhtml:span>
                </xhtml:a>
            </xhtml:p>
            <xhtml:div class="xforms-error-details"/>
        </xhtml:div>
    </xhtml:div>
</xhtml:div>
